description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Muscle Building Row' from the channel Sera Moon Busse.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Competitor vibe.
The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible. The The Competitor vibe means Gamified, leaderboard-driven, full-send energy. This is especially good for Those who need to chase a score or beat their own record..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Push your limits and feel the burn as you power through each set, honing your technique and stamina. Join Sera Moon for a high-intensity session focused on maximizing your power strokes. This workout features 10 powerful strokes at a time, perfect for building muscle and enhancing strength. Get ready to elevate your rowing game and achieve peak performance on the water! Max rhythm: 30, Format: Intervals...
